{"tid":1550104,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實你地有無諗過自殺潮可能係真","createTime":"2019-09-07T14:24:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T15:34:07.000Z","uid":199727,"like":36,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"9f3ff0d428b0c813d55b9936df31ee2a9b4d4ac9","tid":1550104,"uid":199727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T14:24:29.000Z","msg":"呢三個月來 唔同手足都面對種種情緒問題 <br />\n而呢幾個禮拜 企跳既個案真係愈黎愈多<br />\n就算最終被說服繼續活下去 都不斷承受住各種壓力<br />\n呢次自殺潮開始於林鄭撒回既第二日，可能有啲手足覺得辛苦咗三個月先只換來撒回，令佢地覺得徹底失去希望，才決定放棄生命。<br />\n<br />\n應承我，如果你覺得好攰好絕望，請即刻del咗連登同新聞app佢，做返一兩個禮拜港豬。<br />\n<br />\n同時希望各位立即正視手足既情緒問題，多啲主動關心身邊情緒低落既手足，開解同聆聽佢地。<br />\n<br />\n香港人，缺一不可。"},{"pid":"ff1bd4475721049204224bb4c68e98c00f7059de","tid":1550104,"uid":199727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T14:27:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2075b19c98f9164ae784ab0682614576fa563c04","tid":1550104,"uid":199727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T14:29:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"811be2e3b8839e0b29d5d56c576121b2920edd44","tid":1550104,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T14:30:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c12ff8535a343f56a5ae46681483c7beae518e4e","tid":1550104,"uid":199727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T14:30:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"93de5714d1b166a35de92e40cadf8d039895454d","tid":1550104,"uid":236368,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T14:30:57.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過被自殺係真？"},{"pid":"a618dd262750cc482ec8fadd13de63a264970c55","tid":1550104,"uid":8833,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T14:31:48.000Z","msg":"831既人？"},{"pid":"2af10771fa7cbae40414f8fbb5134df28af1e8bf","tid":1550104,"uid":199727,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"93de5714d1b166a35de92e40cadf8d039895454d","tid":1550104,"uid":236368,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T14:30:57.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過被自殺係真？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T14:32:39.000Z","msg":"客觀事實係短短兩日已經有雙位數人去世<br />\n你認為手足情緒問題係必須得以正視"},{"pid":"ab1c845cf5f63e0d1099e4790c9ddba4c03dac21","tid":1550104,"uid":95501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f3ff0d428b0c813d55b9936df31ee2a9b4d4ac9","tid":1550104,"uid":199727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T14:24:29.000Z","msg":"呢三個月來 唔同手足都面對種種情緒問題 <br />\n而呢幾個禮拜 企跳既個案真係愈黎愈多<br />\n就算最終被說服繼續活下去 都不斷承受住各種壓力<br />\n呢次自殺潮開始於林鄭撒回既第二日，可能有啲手足覺得辛苦咗三個月先只換來撒回，令佢地覺得徹底失去希望，才決定放棄生命。<br />\n<br />\n應承我，如果你覺得好攰好絕望，請即刻del咗連登同新聞app佢，做返一兩個禮拜港豬。<br />\n<br />\n同時希望各位立即正視手足既情緒問題，多啲主動關心身邊情緒低落既手足，開解同聆聽佢地。<br />\n<br />\n香港人，缺一不可。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T14:33:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/sanction-hong-kong-government-its-state-terrorism-conducted-prince-edward-train-station-hong-kong-831?fbclid=IwAR067_l3XCORb_zfbsbrOP7_ntJbHF1-Ivy22mNx_bjoUFar8T0a9rxxh_U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fsanction-hong-kong-government-its-state-terrorism-conducted-prince-edward-train-station-hong-kong-831%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR067_l3