normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  屌你老母講你又唔撚聽   唔撚信咪過主囉  又要眾人皆醉我獨醒"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T14:35:29.000Z","msg":"屌你老母啦<br />\n手足情緒問題唔洗正視?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T14:37:45.000Z","msg":"唔洗理佢 一句就屌老母<br />\n有問題"},{"pid":"e5c5c2e6fd5f2f7370fad60cd03c6737d5c51837","tid":1550104,"uid":199727,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T14:38:07.000Z","msg":"你地個撚個就一口咬定一定係被自殺<br />\n咁去到依家有無一個客觀證據證明呢一班人就係被自殺架?<br />\n喺未證明到之前，呢批個案全部仍然係列作自殺案去睇。<br />\n我想問一下 我既建議:關心下身邊手足又得罪咗你地啲乜野<br />\n有無諗過如果萬一係真既自殺潮，你地坐視不理既態度會害死幾多手足"},{"pid":"39547cb51c57b330c33953d4c626847310ccba7c","tid":1550104,"uid":81894,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b2205980d564a2f764f00d7ba2268b2a209c9fd2","tid":1550104,"uid":52520,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30380c062d40e50101c8087b9a5f9e6901c22ffb","tid":1550104,"uid":199727,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c99658f49c3010af2edc241e635b03a13447302b","tid":1550104,"uid":52520,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T14:34:24.000Z","msg":"你不如搵一段歷史 一個地方  可以兩日咁多自殺呢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  屌你老母講你又唔撚聽   唔撚信咪過主囉  又要眾人皆醉我獨醒"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T14:35:29.000Z","msg":"屌你老母啦<br />\n手足情緒問題唔洗正視?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T14:36:42.000Z","msg":"屌你老母你當自己係神定係社工  你係到出Post有撚用？ 知道有手足有情緒問題就帶去搵社工啦  咁撚多聲氣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T14:40:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1300056863502571&amp;id=175011046007164\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D1300056863502571%26id%3D175011046007164&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQC%2FsPRfgRtgRFNgQ5kFpanIU%3D&h=e833dd79\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1300056863502571&amp;id=175011046007164</a><br />\